	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />NWC uses the lockout chip's RESET line in order to initialize the mapper. It would appear that "cutting pin #4" leaves this RESET line intact and still allows games to work properly.
<br />
<br />I suspect, if you tried running the game on a TOP-loader, you would have some problems...

		

		</td>
